data.name: ReadCaseRoleCsePersonCase
data.value: select T1.CAS_NUMBER, T1.CSP_NUMBER, T1.TYPE, T1.CASE_ROLE_ID, T1.START_DATE, T1.END_DATE, T1.EMANCIPATION_DT, T2.TYPE, T2.OUT_OF_WEDLOCK, T2.PAT_ESTAB_IND, T3.INTERSTATE_CASE_ID from CKT_CASE T3 with(readuncommitted) join CKT_CSE_PERSON T2 with(readuncommitted) join CKT_CASE_ROLE T1 with(readuncommitted) on (T2.OUT_OF_WEDLOCK = 'Y') and (T2.NUMB = T1.CSP_NUMBER) and (T1.TYPE = 'CH') and (T1.START_DATE <= @startDate) and (T1.END_DATE >= @endDate) and (T2.NUMB > @numb) and (T2.NUMB between cast(@suppPersonNumber1 as char(10)) and cast(@suppPersonNumber2 as char(10))) on T3.NUMB = T1.CAS_NUMBER order by T1.CSP_NUMBER

data.name: ReadGoodCause
data.value: select top(1) CODE, EFFECTIVE_DATE, DISCONTINUE_DATE, CREATED_TIMESTAMP, CAS_NUMBER, CSP_NUMBER, CRO_TYPE, CRO_IDENTIFIER from CKT_GOOD_CAUSE with(readuncommitted) where (@casNumber = CAS_NUMBER) and (@cspNumber = CSP_NUMBER) and (@croType = CRO_TYPE) and (@croIdentifier = CRO_IDENTIFIER) and (CODE = 'CO') and (CREATED_TIMESTAMP > @createdTimestamp1) and (CREATED_TIMESTAMP < @createdTimestamp2)

data.name: ReadGoodCauseCaseRole
data.value: select T1.CODE, T1.EFFECTIVE_DATE, T1.DISCONTINUE_DATE, T1.CREATED_TIMESTAMP, T1.CAS_NUMBER, T1.CSP_NUMBER, T1.CRO_TYPE, T1.CRO_IDENTIFIER, T2.START_DATE, T2.END_DATE from CKT_CASE_ROLE T2 with(readuncommitted) join CKT_GOOD_CAUSE T1 with(readuncommitted) on (T1.CODE = 'GC') and (T2.CAS_NUMBER = T1.CAS_NUMBER) and (T2.CSP_NUMBER = T1.CSP_NUMBER) and (T2.TYPE = T1.CRO_TYPE) and (T2.CASE_ROLE_ID = T1.CRO_IDENTIFIER) and (T2.TYPE = 'AR') and (@casNumber = T2.CAS_NUMBER) and (T1.EFFECTIVE_DATE <= @effectiveDate) and (T1.DISCONTINUE_DATE >= @effectiveDate) and (T2.START_DATE <= @effectiveDate) and (T2.END_DATE >= @effectiveDate)

data.name: ReadOcse157Data1
data.value: select top(1) max(RUN_NUMBER) from CKT_OCSE157_DATA with(readuncommitted) where (FISCAL_YEAR = @fiscalYear) and (LINE_NUMBER = '04 ')

data.name: ReadOcse157Data2
data.value: select top(1) max(RUN_NUMBER) from CKT_OCSE157_DATA with(readuncommitted) where (FISCAL_YEAR = @fiscalYear) and (LINE_NUMBER = '05 ')

data.name: ReadOcse157Verification1
data.value: select top(1) min(SUPP_PERSON_NUMBER) from CKT_OCSE157_VERIFI with(readuncommitted) where (COLUMN0 <> ' ') and (FISCAL_YEAR = @fiscalYear) and (RUN_NUMBER = @runNumber) and (LINE_NUMBER = '04 ') and (SUPP_PERSON_NUMBER = @suppPersonNumber)

data.name: ReadOcse157Verification2
data.value: select FISCAL_YEAR, RUN_NUMBER, LINE_NUMBER, COLUMN0, CREATED_TIMESTAMP, CASE_NUMBER, SUPP_PERSON_NUMBER, DATE_OF_BIRTH, CHILD_4_DIGIT_SSN from CKT_OCSE157_VERIFI with(readuncommitted) where (COLUMN0 <> ' ') and (FISCAL_YEAR = @fiscalYear) and (RUN_NUMBER = @runNumber) and (LINE_NUMBER = '05 ') and (SUPP_PERSON_NUMBER > @suppPersonNumber1) and (SUPP_PERSON_NUMBER between cast(@suppPersonNumber2 as char(10)) and cast(@suppPersonNumber3 as char(10))) order by SUPP_PERSON_NUMBER
